<!-- CHAPTER 7 -->
<h1 class="chapter" id="ch7">Chapter 7: 32 Devathas — Complete Reference</h1>
<p>The 32 Devathas are divine guardians assigned to the 32 segments of the perimeter of any plot or building. Each Devatha governs a specific aspect of life and bestows auspicious or inauspicious effects depending on what activities are placed in their zone.</p>
<h2 class="section" id="ref-chart">Complete 32 Devatha Reference Chart</h2>
